{"tid":2162145,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"華倫西亞好撚慘 無錢出糧要寫欠單","createTime":"2020-08-18T03:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T06:02:56.000Z","uid":10338,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9cceddd1f99e3316804d1059e04d58d4b757364b","tid":2162145,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:24:42.000Z","msg":"西甲華倫西亞球會實在發不出薪金了，他們給球員們開出了薪金欠單。<br />\n　　據《馬卡報》披露，疫情打擊之下，華倫西亞球會陷入財政困境，無力支付球員薪金。該隊計劃，用欠單的方式來暫時解決問題。週一，球會財政總監伊巴內茲來到訓練場，和球員們進行溝通，並初步宣佈了這一方式。<br />\n　　華倫西亞球會主席阿內爾-梅菲則在公開信中說：「我們必須降低薪金，這意味著合約兩年或更短、薪金較高的球員將被賣掉。」而據西班牙媒體稱，華倫西亞全隊除了荷西-加亞（Jose Gaya）外，其他人都在可供出售的轉會名單上。<br />\n<br />\n對於7月28日才剛上任的新教練沙維-加西亞（Javi Garcia）來說，如何提振球隊士氣，確保球員不分心，恐怕是他首先需要解決的問題。"},{"pid":"ed293910a3cd3deb452a17fd0765bec6bee837b4","tid":2162145,"uid":7854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:27:36.000Z","msg":"咁搞法跌落西乙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a54ff8be52fed4a5fe4da8f6286362b24f8d79e","tid":2162145,"uid":131548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:35:35.000Z","msg":"明明換咗個老細 點解又係越嚟越窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7da0cc1186844d63350d907a8cecd06e5f11a4","tid":2162145,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:36:12.000Z","msg":"華西<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effe1bafd1d472e764c6204c305d7b62991e91d2","tid":2162145,"uid":351028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"各大球會去執平野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc861527b78fd6c2ce3293cc3bc1d5e706cba8c8","tid":2162145,"uid":298237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-1